{"tid":1613998,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"雙螢幕的 Surface Duo 是微軟手機的回歸作","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:16:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"497a13c84346f342ea5f29a7b758b55bf4fcc528","tid":1613998,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"微軟和手機市場間的關係總是經歷著反覆，在經歷了 Windows Phone / Windows 10 Mobile 時代的失意之後，睽違行動行業已久的他們現在終於決定要再度回歸了。緊接著今晚發表會的重頭戲 Surface Neo 之後，微軟也玩了一齣「One More Thing」，在活動最後公佈了全新的 Surface Duo。這是一款採用了跟 Neo 相似雙螢幕設計的產品，但更重要的一點是，其運行的系統已經換成了 Android。<br />\n<br />\n根據目前已知的情報，Duo 的中間設有一根 360 度的轉軸，兩側的螢幕均為 5.6 吋。在有來電進來的時候，你可以將其折疊成螢幕背靠背的狀態來接聽。雖說在現場沒有示範，但不出意外的話 Duo 除了雙螢幕以外，應該也會提供單螢幕的常規 Android UI。此外和許多今年問世的旗艦機一樣，微軟目前也是為 Duo 選擇了 Snapdragon 855 晶片。不過考慮到這款手機和 Surface Neo 一樣，都是預計於明年聖誕節上市，期間會不會有規格上的變動，目前還不太好說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-10%2F81962d70-e52e-11e9-8cfb-144817b6b93d&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=451c28cd35f216d29204fd0c88a2bdad30045e5e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-10%252F81962d70-e52e-11e9-8cfb-144817b6b93d%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D451c28cd35f216d29204fd0c88a2bdad30045e5e&h=ecfa903f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，在發表到發售的這一年準備期中，微軟也希望能有更多開發者會針對 Duo 的特性做出一些軟體上的最佳化。不過就目前來看，這方面的努力可能還是很難跳出類似 Galaxy Fold 的範疇。微軟手機上一次失敗的主因便是軟體，這次回歸若想有不同的結果，面前應該還是以有很長的路要走啊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2019/10/02/microsoft-surface-duo-android-phone-official/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2Fmicrosoft-surface-duo-android-phone-official%2F&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXwCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=9f146fd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2019/10/02/microsoft-surface-duo-android-phone-official/</a>"},{"pid":"fda5eb520df0e5a49eaa6beec79f41a8eb185d13","tid":1613998,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-10%2Fc9f39c00-e52f-11e9-9bdf-52adf2c784f9&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=177579c0e3a96c75f0bffdb629505ed6d3d85cc4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-10%252Fc9f39c00-e52f-11e9-9bdf-52adf2c784f9%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D177579c0e3a96c75f0bffdb629505ed6d3d85cc4&h=4b92de5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f4607361fb4f6af02ef639c376ab616042cfe7a","tid":1613998,"uid":65186,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"唔想再比機會佢。<br />\n<br />\n利申：前寶藥黨"},{"pid":"8fac88b25dbc531b12dffceb3fab373d0a0545e7","tid":1613998,"uid":113922,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"注定收皮，個款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5dbefbd704ad31f2857fe3e6cd930e3f49fdb6","tid":1613998,"uid":263058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae135813b1f592d402e9211f2ea682e5b5ecc242","tid":1613998,"uid":181531,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"Microsoft hardware<br />\n一睇就知好易壞"},{"pid":"d7dd2723838567366442f03b584783de637b5532","tid":1613998,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae135813b1f592d402e9211f2ea682e5b5ecc242","tid":1613998,"uid":181531,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-0